ting partner??</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I remade my old monk.  With gear he has 120 strength and 120 stamina.  With a few more items I can get 150 stamina.  All that extra HP will help out in the long run.  Also regenerate helps a lot.<br>
