n't taunt it off, and I can take the damage.  We have to pay attention to where we choose to fight, but it works.  We're both 41, and we've hunted together since 20, sometimes as a pair, sometimes with a cleric or a druid.</font><P>Loredena Frisealach Mainacier<BR>
